    <p class="section-label">Submissions</p>
    <h2>How to Submit</h2>
    <p>
      To add a model to the leaderboard, please open a
      <a href="https://github.com/utahnlp/infinite-science-gym/issues" target="_blank">GitHub issue</a>
      including the information below, or email us at
      <a href="mailto:oliver.bentham@utah.edu">oliver.bentham@utah.edu</a>.
      Self-reported scores are accepted but marked with † until independently
      verified. We reserve the right to remove entries that cannot be reproduced.
    </p>
    <p>
      Include: model name, organization, access type (open / API),
      parameter count (if known), a link to the model card or paper, and your
      reported scores. We may independently verify results before listing.
    </p>

